    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sundials that first appeared in ancient Rome, used to tell time by utilizing the moving shadow of the sun cast upon a marked surface.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
